page.title: 10 Boy's Diet in West Stafford
page.content: Kevin and Craig have written down the food they ate during a typical day. Kevin ate shreddies and drank a cup of tea. At 10.30am he had some crisps bought by his Mum.One and a half hours after his dinner he had toast and pop.When he got home from school he had fish fingers,chips and peas.after he had sandwiches and a cup of tea. Graig had Weetabix,tea and toast.At about 10.30am he ate a packet of crisps.At dinner time he had Corn- flakes and a cup of tea.At tea time he had chips,beans and cottage pie.For supper he had a drink of tea and some sandwiches.
